         <anchor xml:id="c56-0108.08"/> 
         <lb n="c56-0108_main_2"/>Nothing is more painful <mod>
            <add place="sublinear">
               <metamark function="insert">^</metamark>
            </add>
            <add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear">than</add>
         </mod> when the <lb n="c56-0108_main_3"/>mind has been worked up by a <add place="intralinear">quick</add> 
         <lb n="c56-0108_main_4"/>
         <del rend="strikethrough">S</del> succession of events, <delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0108.01"/>for a dead calm <lb n="c56-0108_main_5"/>of inaction and certainty to<anchor xml:id="c56-0108.01"/>
