            <add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear">and</add>
         </mod> 
         <lb n="c56-0108_main_6"/>deprives the <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">mind</del>
            <add place="superlinear">soul</add>
         </mod> both of hope or fear. <lb n="c56-0108_main_7"/>Justine died— She rested. <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">But</del>
            <add place="superlinear">&amp;</add>
         </mod> I was alive <lb n="c56-0108_main_8"/>the blood flowed freely in my veins but <lb n="c56-0108_main_9"/>a weight of despair &amp; remorse pressed <lb n="c56-0108_main_10"/>on my heart which nothing could remove–<delSpan rend="vertical_line" spanTo="#c56-0108.04"/> 
         <lb n="c56-0108_main_11"/>our house was a house of mourning– <lb n="c56-0108_main_12"/>My fathers health was deeply shaken by <lb n="c56-0108_main_13"/>the horror of the recent events; <w ana="start"/>Eliza<lb n="c56-0108_main_14"/>beth<w ana="end"/> was sad and desponding– She no longer <lb n="c56-0108_main_15"/>took delight in her ordinary <w ana="start"/>occupa<lb n="c56-0108_main_16"/>tions<w ana="end"/> all pleasure seemed to her <w ana="start"/>sacri<lb n="c56-0108_main_17"/>ledge<w ana="end"/> towards the dead— eternal woe <lb n="c56-0108_main_18"/>and tears she then thought was the <lb n="c56-0108_main_19"/>just tribute she ought to pay to <w ana="start"/>inno<lb n="c56-0108_main_20"/>cence<w ana="end"/> thus blasted &amp; <del rend="strikethrough">destroyed</del>
         <anchor xml:id="c56-0108.04"/>
         <retrace cause="unclear">S</retrace>leep fled <lb n="c56-0108_main_21"/>from my eyes. I wandered like an <lb n="c56-0108_main_22"/>evil spirit for I <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">done</del>
            <add place="sublinear">
               <metamark function="insert">^</metamark>
