            <add place="sublinear">
               <metamark function="insert">^</metamark>
            </add>
            <add place="superlinear">horrible,</add>
         </mod> and <del rend="smear">
            <add place="superlinear">hor</add>
         </del> more much more (I <lb n="c56-0108_main_24"/>persuaded my self) was yet in store. <lb n="c56-0108_main_25"/>Yet my heart overflowed with <w ana="start"/>kind<lb n="c56-0108_main_26"/>ness<w ana="end"/> and <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">benevolence</del>
            <add place="superlinear">goodness</add>
         </mod> – I had begun life <lb n="c56-0108_main_27"/>with benevolent intentions and thirsted for <lb n="c56-0108_main_28"/>the moment when I <mod>
            <add place="sublinear">
               <metamark function="insert">^</metamark>
