         </mod> recovered from the <lb n="c56-0109_main_13"/>first shock it had sustained. I shunned <lb n="c56-0109_main_14"/>the face of man; all sound of joy or <lb n="c56-0109_main_15"/>complacency was torture to me<add hand="#pbs" place="intralinear">;</add> Solitude <lb n="c56-0109_main_16"/>was my only consolation deep, dark, <del rend="strikethrough">night</del> 
