         <add place="intralinear">&amp; </add>suffering Elizabeth whom I tenderly <lb n="c56-0111_main_11"/>loved, and whose existence was bound <lb n="c56-0111_main_12"/>up in mine. And then I thought also <lb n="c56-0111_main_13"/>of my father and surviving brother; <del rend="strikethrough">And</del> 
         <lb n="c56-0111_main_14"/>should I not by my base desertion leave <lb n="c56-0111_main_15"/>them exposed &amp; unprotected to the <lb n="c56-0111_main_16"/>mali<mod>
        
