               <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_1"/>
               <metamark function="displacement">
                  <hi rend="sup">X</hi>
               </metamark>There was <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_2"/>always scope <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_3"/>for fear so <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_4"/>long as any <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_5"/>thing that <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_6"/>I loved remained <lb n="c56-0112_c56-0112.02_7"/>alive.<anchor xml:id="c56-0112.03"/>
            </zone>
         </add>
      My <lb n="c56-0112_main_3"/>abhorrence of this fiend cannot be <lb n="c56-0112_main_4"/>conceived – When I thought of him I <lb n="c56-0112_main_5"/>gnashed my teeth my eyes became <w ana="start"/>inflam<lb n="c56-0112_main_6"/>ed<w ana="end"/> and I ardently wished to extinguish <lb n="c56-0112_main_7"/>that life which I had so thoughtlessly <lb n="c56-0112_main_8"/>bestowed. When I <del rend="strikethrough">though</del> reflected on his <lb n="c56-0112_main_9"/>crimes and malice, my hatred and <lb n="c56-0112_main_10"/>revenge burst all bounds of moderation <lb n="c56-0112_main_11"/>
         <delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0112.04"/>I wished but to see him again that
      I <lb n="c56-0112_main_12"/>might<anchor xml:id="c56-0112.04"/> I would have made a pilgrimage <lb n="c56-0112_main_13"/>to the highest<add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear">peak of the</add> Andes could I when
      there <lb n="c56-0112_main_14"/>have precipitated him to their <mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough">foot</del>
            <add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear">base</add>
